{"list":[{"title":"目的","data":"<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:28px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\"><span style=\"color:#000000\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">认识变压器；</span></span></span></span></span></p>\n\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:28px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\"><span style=\"color:#000000\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">探究变压器线圈两端电压与匝数的关系。</span></span></span></span></span></p>"},{"title":"原理","data":"<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:28px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\"><span style=\"color:#000000\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">互感。</span></span></span></span></span></p>"},{"title":"器材","data":"<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:28px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\"><span style=\"color:#000000\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">学生电源、变压器、数字万用表</span></span></span></span></span></p>"},{"title":"步骤","data":"<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:26px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\"><span style=\"color:#000000\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">1.调整学生电源电压为</span>10V<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">，将学生电源交流输出端分别接在变压器原线圈的&ldquo;</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">0</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">&rdquo;端和&ldquo;</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">8</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">&rdquo;端；</span></span></span></span></span></p>\n\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:26px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\"><span style=\"color:#000000\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">2.万用表选择交流电压档，两端分别接变压器副线圈接线柱</span>&ldquo;<span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">0</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">&rdquo;端和&ldquo;</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">4</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">&rdquo;端，打开电源，读出万用表示数；</span></span></span></span></span></p>\n\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:26px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\"><span style=\"color:#000000\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">3.关闭电源，将万用表分别接在变压器副线圈的</span>&ldquo;<span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">0</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">&rdquo;端和&ldquo;</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">1</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">&rdquo;端；</span></span></span></span></span></p>\n\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:26px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\"><span style=\"color:#000000\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">4.打开电源，读出此时万用表示数。</span></span></span></span></span></p>"},{"title":"结论","data":"<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:28px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\"><span style=\"background-color:#ffffff\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\"><span style=\"color:#000000\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">变压器原副线圈的电压比等于原副线圈的匝数之比。</span></span></span></span></span></span></p>"},{"title":"补充","data":"<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:28px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\"><span style=\"color:#000000\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">理想变压器满足，<em><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman,Times,serif\">U</span></em><sub>1</sub>:<em><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman,Times,serif\">U</span></em><sub>2</sub>=<em><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman,Times,serif\">n</span></em><sub>1</sub>:<em><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman,Times,serif\">n</span></em><sub>2</sub>，<span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman,Times,serif\"><em>I</em></span><sub>1</sub>:<span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman,Times,serif\"><em>I</em></span><sub>2</sub>=<em><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman,Times,serif\">n</span></em><sub>2</sub>:<em><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman,Times,serif\">n</span></em><sub>1</sub>，<span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman,Times,serif\"><em>P</em></span><sub>1</sub>=<span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman,Times,serif\"><em>P</em></span><sub>2</sub>。</span></span></span></span></span></p>"}],"x":0,"y":0,"width":600,"height":600}